author: coheigea
msg: [WSS-257] - Avoid converting SOAP Body to DOM unless necessary
- Added a "CallbackLookup" interface, and implementation, to find a DOM element
- A CallbackLookup implementation can be set on the processing side, with the aim of only having to convert the SOAP Body to DOM when it's needed.
